"linux:~ # rpm -i /tmp/otrs-xxx.rpm\n"
"otrs                        "
"##################################################\n"
"Check OTRS user (/etc/passwd)... otrs exists.\n"
"\n"
"Next steps:\n"
"\n"
"[SuSEconfig]\n"
" Execute 'SuSEconfig' to configure the web server.\n"
"\n"
