msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:426
msgid ""
"You can search for a registered customer, or edit their settings by clicking "
"on their name. You also have the possibility to change the customer "
"back-end, for further information please refer to the chapter about <link "
"linkend=\"external-backends\">external back-ends</link>."
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:430
msgid ""
"To create a new customer account, click on the \"Add customer\" button (see "
"Figure below). Some of the fields are mandatory, i.e., they have to contain "
"values, so if you leave one of those empty, it will be highlighted in red."
msgstr ""

