#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/adminarea.xml:656
msgid "Signatures"
msgstr ""

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:659
msgid ""
"Another text module for a response is the signature. Signatures can be "
"linked to a queue, as described in the section about the <link "
"linkend=\"adminarea-queue\">queues</link>. Only if a signature is linked to "
"a queue will it be included into the response text. Through the "
"\"Signatures\" link of the Admin page, you can manage the signatures in your "
"system (see Figure below)."
